## 🤖 3. Google Play Store (Android) Regulations

Google’s rules are very similar to Apple’s, but a bit more relaxed.

### 📘 Google Policy Center:

Link: [Google Play Developer Policy Center](mdc:https:/support.google.com/googleplay/android-developer/answer/113469#content)

Key points:

### ✅ Privacy

* Must show a **Privacy Policy**.
* Follow **Google Play Data Safety Section**.
* If targeting EU, **comply with GDPR** and DSA.

### ✅ Content Policies

* No harmful or illegal content.
* Must moderate user-generated content.
* Must allow **user blocking**, **reporting**, and **content removal**.

### ✅ In-App Purchases

* Use **Google Play Billing** for digital goods.
* No linking to outside payment systems for in-app items.

